-- 11. Sittingbourne × AI Automation
INSERT INTO public.local_content (service_slug, town_slug, intro_paragraph, local_context, competition_landscape, success_approach, local_stats, pain_points, solutions, faqs, layout_variant)
VALUES (
  'ai-automation',
  'sittingbourne',
  'Sittingbourne businesses are growing but their operational capacity is not keeping pace. The trades sector is stretched thin by increasing demand from new housing developments. Industrial firms at Eurolink manage complex operations with lean teams. Retail and service businesses handle rising customer volumes with the same staffing levels. Traditional automation handles the simple, repetitive tasks. AI automation goes further, introducing intelligent decision-making into your operations. Systems that can read and classify customer enquiries, draft appropriate responses, route jobs to the right team member based on skill and availability, and flag potential issues before they become problems. For Sittingbourne businesses running at capacity, AI automation provides the operational intelligence of a much larger organisation without the headcount.',
  'Sittingbourne''s business environment is characterised by practical, hands-on operations where efficiency directly impacts profitability. Trades managing multiple residential projects simultaneously need intelligent scheduling and communication. Eurolink-based logistics and manufacturing firms handle complex supply chains where delays cascade expensively. Retail businesses near The Forum balance inventory, customer service, and online orders with minimal staff. The common challenge is that operational complexity has outgrown team capacity, and hiring in the current market is both expensive and difficult.',
  'AI automation awareness in Sittingbourne is minimal, creating a genuine early-adopter advantage. While basic software tools are widely used, intelligent automation that applies AI to classify, decide, and generate outputs is virtually unknown in the local business community. The few businesses nationally that have adopted AI automation report significant competitive advantages in responsiveness, accuracy, and operational capacity.',
  'We implement AI automation for Sittingbourne businesses by identifying the tasks where intelligent processing delivers the biggest time and accuracy gains. For trades, this might mean AI that reads enquiry emails, classifies the job type, and drafts appropriate responses automatically. For industrial firms, it could mean intelligent quality checks or automated report generation. Every implementation starts with your actual Sittingbourne operations and builds from there.',
  '{"population": 63000, "borough": "Swale", "business_districts": ["Eurolink Industrial Estate", "The Forum", "High Street"], "key_fact": "Lean operational teams combined with growing demand create ideal conditions for AI automation impact"}',
